CheckIssuing,is,a,high,volume,check,writing,organization,that,aims,to,facilitate,the,payment,process,Some,of,the,services,include,monthly,statements,customized,checks,and,dedicated,account,representatives,To,focus,on,the,solution,CheckIssuing,offers,aggressive,volume,based,pricing,security,envelopes,and,API,integration,The,CheckIssuing,API,allows,to,securely,import,data,directly,into,the,company,s,systems,to,process,payments,To,use,the,API,it,is,suggested,to,create,an,account,After,receiving,an,API,key,the,documents,will,serve,as,a,guide,to,begin,with,the,implementation,This,API,can,be,particularly,useful,to,access,account,balances,submit,new,deposits,and,submit,new,payment,requests